---
layout: layouts/base.njk
section: Ruben Schuckit's Website
---

{% set js %}
  {% include "assets/js/home.js" %}
{% endset %}

<div class="container p-3">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-2 mb-3">
      <picture class="photo-me">
        <source media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="static/img/my_picture.jpg"/>
        <img class="rounded mx-auto d-block" src="static/img/my_picture_small.jpg"/>
      </picture>
      <img class="rounded d-none photo-noogler" src="static/img/noogler.gif"/>
      <div class="mt-1 p-lg-3 p-1 d-flex justify-content-between border-lg">
        <a href="https://github.com/rubenschuckit" rel="noopener" target="_blank" class="no-link-decoration">
          <img height="20" width="20" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@v2/icons/github.svg"/>
        </a>
        <a href="http://twitter.com/rubenschuckit" rel="noopener" target="_blank" class="no-link-decoration">
          <img height="20" width="20" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@v2/icons/twitter.svg"/>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/schuckit/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" class="no-link-decoration">
          <img height="20" width="20" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@v2/icons/linkedin.svg"/>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-5">
      <div class="text-center text-md-left">
        {{ layoutContent | safe }}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-5 d-none d-md-block">
      <img class="rounded" src="static/img/bayarea.jpg"/>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-center mt-5">My Interests</h1>
  <hr/>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Viola</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div style="background-color: rgb(187, 242, 211)" class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block"></div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>I began playing viola in 6th grade and still play today. I put most of my performances on my <a href="https://www.youtube.com/user/rschuckit" rel="noopener" target="_blank">YouTube Channel</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="static/img/viola.jpg"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Aviation</h2>
    <div class="row flex-row-reverse">
      <div style="background-color: rgb(2, 94, 115)" class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block"></div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>Ever since I was little I've been obsessed with aviation. I was lucky to pursue pilot training and received my private pilot license before going off to college.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="static/img/flying.jpg"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center">Coding</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div style="background-color: rgb(189, 217, 176)" class="col-md-1 d-none d-md-block"></div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>I took my first computer science course in high school and stayed with it all through college and into my professional life. This site is a testing ground I use to try out cool things.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="static/img/software-engineering.jpg"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script defer>
  {{ js | jsmin | safe }}
</script>
